cv, cf, mfunc = cfcf
mfunc.run(locals())
if mfunc.exception is not None or not mfunc.passed:
    print('\n', mfunc.name)
    print('  ', mfunc.runline)
    print('  ', mfunc.testline)
    if mfunc.exception is None:
        mfunc.exception = ValueError(
            'Calculated values are different from the expected matlab results.'
            )
    raise mfunc.exception
else:
    print(mfunc.name)
    assert mfunc.passed
